# Plan E T1: agent/decision is a Windows junction (POSIX symlink in CI) to
# predictive-mcdm-defi/decision -- created out-of-band by `mklink /J`.
# git's Windows-port mishandles junctions; gitignoring keeps the zero-drift
# guarantee intact on fresh clones. Recovery: see agent/RUNBOOK.md.
agent/decision/

